{"tid":191642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女王迪詩：時下年輕人「愛走捷徑」！","createTime":"2017-04-08T05:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T08:50:49.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3fd7dcef98d43c7e112ed92939c8adeb424e5f","tid":191642,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"有個剛畢業的年輕人某天突然找我，說非常崇拜我，又是才女又是美女，古往今來無人能及，我想嘔，接着他問我能否幫他在Facebook出個post宣傳他那場表演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心裏很替他悲哀，這些核突行為就等你變成喪盡理想的中坑才做吧，怎麼剛畢業就這般墮落？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想他一定已用盡所有方法，迫不得已才講這些違心話，其實他不用這樣說，我認為值得幫的也會幫，我二話不說就替他在Facebook宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他說為表謝意請吃飯，問我幾時得閒，我答下星期四，他竟然不回覆，人間蒸發了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年後他某天突然在我的Facebook留言說才女美女天上有地下無blah blah blah，接着果然又發私訊來提出要求，他最近一場表演又滯銷了。"},{"pid":"fa73af9b53e5f0b2209e878c31847ddea93c53f5","tid":191642,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"正常人都愛走捷徑㗎啦"},{"pid":"c41e0787f2c5b735e3ff977d9bb9b0cc0a6df912","tid":191642,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"我認識一個剛畢業的男生，每逢周末必定陪父母飲茶，說話十分乖巧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我讚他孝順，他竟私底下坦白地說：「我最憎飲茶，但沒辦法呀，我老竇得一層樓而我有三兄弟，將來他只能把物業留給我們其中一人。」<br />\n<br />\n我看儍了眼，他說這話時眉飛色舞，彷彿在炫耀自己多麼聰明。&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貪錢沒問題，問題在於現在不流行靠自己的力量去賺自己應得的，而是去計算身邊的人有沒有利用價值。<br />\n<br />\n怪獸家長逼孩子入名校是為他們將來「鋪路」，結識富三代同學，自小學識同有錢人「埋堆」，展開精采人生。"},{"pid":"78bf427136fdd3868dae6b01a23e4a44e9d6794f","tid":191642,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ad486277f5e9560f2850ad6bdb63a412b6ebd2c","tid":191642,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美女圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20150119/large/19fj505p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20150119%2Flarge%2F19fj505p.jpg&h=134c3428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係王迪詩"},{"pid":"e92b1cf08a624897ae5b125b177775de7f964b2f","tid":191642,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"有咩舉世科技唔係當時既人走捷徑研究出黎 ?"},{"pid":"ae8fab23515c687bf94bd894398c9e5f64ff1493","tid":191642,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"065cd3d8dece3d717964647876c46aa741160e4d","tid":191642,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"港嬸定港女"},{"pid":"3b25d68493cda3ee52bb382e976fee0433e0cba2","tid":191642,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港嬸定港女</blockquote><br />\n老港女"},{"pid":"7f03cb1ad5c2faa5ff052dc14d05dd43c2449ff9","tid":191642,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"假扮律師仲未被人拉？"},{"pid":"5560c9fadf2a5773cef537fd5ee30a4c2af93532","tid":191642,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"不關愛不愛<br />\n而是很多仆街一出生就走捷徑."},{"pid":"b993b250efa01324c01b141f095332cee4f465cf","tid":191642,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假扮律師仲未被人拉？</blockquote><br />\n佢有？"},{"pid":"7e6f031f4d590f907d02863245ec8e2c6e2d99b2","tid":191642,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假扮律師仲未被人拉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncheck到無係law soc / bar 註冊咩?"},{"pid":"2955c66a483afc3b8336e64a3b276aef747d2ee7","tid":191642,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"崇洋老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji